    All Classes and Interfaces

    Classes
    Class
    Description
    CompressedTrie
    A compressed trie data structure for efficient string storage and retrieval.
    CompressedTrieNode
    Represents a single node in a compressed trie data structure.
    Dictionary
    Manages a dictionary of words stored in a compressed trie data structure.
    Edge
    Represents an edge in a compressed trie connecting a parent node to a child node.
    Menu
    Interactive command-line menu for the autocomplete and word analysis system.
    MinHeap
    A min-heap implementation for prioritizing strings based on importance values.
    PrefixAnalyzer
    Analyzes word prefixes in a compressed trie to provide autocomplete and prediction features.
    RobinHoodHashtable
    A hashtable implementation using Robin Hood hashing for efficient collision resolution.
    SinglyLinkedList
    A singly linked list implementation that stores Edge objects.
